    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AuthController
    The AuthController handles authentication and registration operations.
    AuthenticationCustomException
    The AuthenticationCustomException is a custom runtime exception used to represent authentication-related errors within the application.
    BackendApplication
     
    BadRequestException
    BadRequestException is a custom exception class used to represent a bad request error.
    CafeteriaController
    The CafeteriaController serves as the RESTful API entry point for managing cafeterias.
    CafeteriaDTO
    The CafeteriaDTO is a Data Transfer Object used to encapsulate data related to a cafeteria entity for both input (creation/update) and output (response).
    CafeteriaEntity
    CafeteriaEntity is a JPA entity that represents a cafeteria in the database.
    CafeteriaMapper
    CafeteriaMapper is a utility class used for mapping between CafeteriaEntity and CafeteriaDTO.
    CafeteriaRepository
    CafeteriaRepository is a repository interface for accessing and managing CafeteriaEntity objects.
    CafeteriaService
    CafeteriaService is a service interface that defines core operations for managing cafeterias in the system.
    CafeteriaServiceImpl
    CafeteriaServiceImpl is a service class that implements CafeteriaService.
    CorsConfig
    The CorsConfig class is a Spring configuration component that defines global CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing) settings for the application.
    CustomUserDetails
    The CustomUserDetails class is a custom implementation of Spring Security's UserDetails interface.
    CustomUserDetailsServiceImpl
    CustomUserDetailsServiceImpl is a service class that implements UserDetailsService.
    DataMappingException
    DataMappingException is a custom exception class that extends BadRequestException.
    EmailService
    The EmailService interface defines the contract for sending email notifications.
    EmailServiceImpl
    The EmailServiceImpl class provides the implementation of the EmailService interface using Spring's JavaMailSender to send plain text email messages.
    GlobalExceptionHandler
    GlobalExceptionHandler is a global exception handler for handling various types of exceptions thrown in the application.
    JwtAuthenticationFilter
    The JwtAuthenticationFilter is a Spring Security filter that handles JWT-based authentication for incoming HTTP requests.
    JWTUserDTO
    The JWTUserDTO is a Data Transfer Object used to encapsulate user information required for JWT token generation and authentication processes.
    JWTUserMapper
    The JWTUserMapper is a utility class responsible for converting a UserEntity into a JWTUserDTO.
    JwtUtil
    The JwtUtil component handles all JWT-related operations such as token generation, validation, parsing claims, and extracting user information.
    LoginRequestDTO
    The LoginRequestDTO is a Data Transfer Object used for user authentication requests.
    NotFoundException
    The NotFoundException is an abstract base class used for defining custom exceptions when a requested resource is not found.
    OrderController
    The OrderController serves as the RESTful API entry point for managing orders.
    OrderDTO
    The OrderDTO is a Data Transfer Object used to represent order data exchanged between the backend and frontend.
    OrderEntity
    OrderEntity is an entity class representing an order in the system.
    OrderMapper
    The OrderMapper is a utility class used for converting between OrderEntity and OrderDTO.
    OrderProductDTO
    The OrderProductDTO is a Data Transfer Object that represents the association between an order and a specific product.
    OrderProductEntity
    OrderProductEntity is an entity class that represents the association between an order and a product.
    OrderProductMapper
    OrderProductMapper is a utility class used for mapping between OrderProductEntity and OrderProductDTO.
    OrderProductRepository
    The OrderProductRepository provides database access for OrderProductEntity using Spring Data JPA.
    OrderRepository
    The OrderRepository interface provides data access methods for OrderEntity using Spring Data JPA.
    OrderService
    OrderService is an interface that defines the methods for managing order-related operations.
    OrderServiceImpl
    OrderServiceImpl is the service-layer implementation of the OrderService interface.
    OrderStatusDTO
    Data transfer object (DTO) representing the status of an order.
    OrderStatusEnum
    OrderStatusEnum is an enumeration representing the possible statuses of an order.
    PasswordController
    The PasswordController provides RESTful endpoints for password reset functionality.
    PasswordResetService
    The PasswordResetService interface defines the contract for handling password reset functionality.
    PasswordResetServiceImpl
    PasswordResetServiceImpl is a service class that implements PasswordResetService.
    PasswordResetToken
    PasswordResetToken is an entity class representing a token used for password reset.
    PasswordResetTokenRepository
    PasswordResetTokenRepository is a repository interface for accessing and managing PasswordResetToken entities.
    ProductController
    The ProductController serves as the RESTful API entry point for managing products.
    ProductDTO
    The ProductDTO is a Data Transfer Object that encapsulates data related to a product offered in a cafeteria.
    ProductEntity
    ProductEntity is an entity class representing a product in the system.
    ProductMapper
     
    ProductRepository
    ProductRepository is a repository interface for accessing and managing ProductEntity objects.
    ProductService
    ProductService is an interface that defines methods for managing products.
    ProductServiceImpl
    ProductServiceImpl is a service class that implements ProductService.
    ProductTypeEnum
    The ProductTypeEnum defines the available categories for products offered by a cafeteria.
    RegisterUserDTO
    Data transfer object (DTO) for registering a new user.
    RegisterUserMapper
    RegisterUserMapper is a utility class used for mapping between RegisterUserDTO and UserEntity.
    ResetPasswordDTO
    The ResetPasswordDTO is a Data Transfer Object used during the password reset process.
    ResourceNotFoundException
    The ResourceNotFoundException is a concrete subclass of NotFoundException used to indicate that a generic resource was not found in the system.
    ReviewController
    The ReviewController serves as the RESTful API entry point for managing reviews.
    ReviewDTO
    Data transfer object (DTO) representing a review.
    ReviewEntity
    ReviewEntity is an entity class representing a review left by a user for a cafeteria.
    ReviewMapper
    ReviewMapper is a utility class used for mapping between ReviewEntity and ReviewDTO.
    ReviewRepository
    ReviewRepository is a repository interface for accessing and managing ReviewEntity objects.
    ReviewService
    ReviewService is an interface that defines the methods for handling review-related operations.
    ReviewServiceImpl
    ReviewServiceImpl is class that implements ReviewService.
    RoleDTO
    Data transfer object (DTO) representing a role.
    RoleEntity
    RoleEntity is an entity class representing a role assigned to a user.
    RoleMapper
    The RoleMapper class provides utility methods for converting between RoleEntity and RoleDTO.
    RoleRepository
    RoleRepository is a repository interface for accessing and managing RoleEntity objects.
    SecurityConfig
    The SecurityConfig class configures Spring Security for the application.
    SecurityRoleHelper
    The SecurityRoleHelper class provides a static utility method for checking if the currently authenticated user has any of the specified roles.
    SwaggerConfig
    The SwaggerConfig class configures the Swagger/OpenAPI documentation for the application.
    TestData
     
    UpdateUserDTO
    The UpdateUserDTO is a Data Transfer Object used for updating user account information.
    UpdateUserMapper
    The UpdateUserMapper is a utility class responsible for converting a UserEntity into an UpdateUserDTO.
    UserAlreadyExistsException
    UserAlreadyExistsException is a custom exception class that extends BadRequestException.
    UserController
    The UserController serves as the RESTful API entry point for managing users.
    UserDTO
    Data transfer object (DTO) representing a user.
    UserEntity
    UserEntity is an entity class that represents a user in the system.
    UserMapper
    UserMapper is a utility class used for mapping between UserEntity and UserDTO.
    UserRepository
    The UserRepository provides database access methods for UserEntity using Spring Data JPA.
    UserService
    UserService is an interface that defines the methods for managing user-related operations.
    UserServiceImpl
    UserServiceImpl is class that implements UserService.
